    <p id="book2">I throw my hair in a messy bun and throw my new Panic! Shirt I got last week during a Hot Topic run with my best friend Luke. I make my way to the bathroom in the hall and sloppily do my eyeliner. Its crooked but I don’t care. After spraying some cucumber melon bath and body works, I make my way down the stairs hearing some voices coming from the living room. Odd. It’s 7AM on a school day not even my alcoholic mother would be here.</p>

    <h2 onclick="toggleText('book2')">Chapter 3: A Room of One's Own</h2>
    <p id="book2">Insert your text for Chapter 3 here.</p>

    <script>
        function toggleText(bookId) {
            var text = document.getElementById(bookId);
            if (text.style.display === "none") {
                text.style.display = "block";
            } else {
                text.style.display = "none";
            }
        }
    </script>
